{"tid":295241,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個生活用到既博弈論","createTime":"2017-06-23T14:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T20:51:12.000Z","uid":76542,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d40554eccfe67a0c100bc32a3f9565d121d7f0b9","tid":295241,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"「囚徒困局」係人都識唔講啦<br />\n<br />\n第一 <br />\n<br />\n如果你去菜場買菜<br />\n<br />\n當你對某種菜的質量、口味等有疑慮時<br />\n<br />\n賣菜的阿姨常會講：&ldquo;你放心，我一直會係度賣&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n這句話其實包含了&ldquo;博弈論&rdquo;思想<br />\n<br />\n我賣，你們買，是一個次數無限的重復博弈<br />\n<br />\n我今天騙了你，<br />\n<br />\n你們今后就不會再來我這兒買了<br />\n<br />\n所以我不會騙你<br />\n<br />\n菜的質量、口味肯定沒問題。<br />\n<br />\n而你在聽了阿姨的上述一句話後<br />\n<br />\n常常也會常常也會打消疑慮，買菜回家。"},{"pid":"7d683bbb886ab31e6fdcf12456208e6119067307","tid":295241,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"more?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a944fc47996b4d27ce32a691f896c588871b45","tid":295241,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:57:39.000Z","msg":"唔識中文？后乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d284acc332b37bf865bec4cb3a3b28fb48b7465f","tid":295241,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"a0c860a984ddc36079053987f9331d942924607f","tid":295241,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:20:32.000Z","msg":":thinking:"},{"pid":"16620a97a7bf8e5e69bffe65d7bb5c83ef2e2843","tid":295241,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:22:40.000Z","msg":"冇了?"},{"pid":"e9ae13810c45a789fc968b091897ec58912ffb17","tid":295241,"uid":121278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:32:01.000Z","msg":"其實呢個係蜈蚣博弈 囚徒困境係單次嘅博弈"},{"pid":"04df66794d276c0da100a5477021e5c83850fbdc","tid":295241,"uid"